Section Title: ## Find The Latest and Best Events in Bengaluru Today! > How to book an event online?
Content:
Bookmyshow offers a simple, yet seamless experience for browsing, sorting, and booking handpicked events. Just click on the upcoming events of your choice, make the payment through one of the many payment gateways, and you’re good to go!
Consider Bookmyshow as a one-stop-shop for all your live entertainment cravings. You have an option to filter the latest events according to category so you can find the same in the favourite category. You can also filter the genre so you can experience comedy, music, action and more, artists for you to watch your favourite performer or venue so you can find the closest events to your home.
Section Title: ## Find The Latest and Best Events in Bengaluru Today! > ... > Top 3 Events Categories
Content:
Live events are thoughtfully divided into three main categories.
**Comedy events-** If you like to tickle your funny bone, comic relief can be your go-to option. Find the latest [](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/comedy-shows-Bengaluru) [comedy events](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/comedy-shows-bengaluru) by some of Bengaluru’s best comedians. Catch them in **Bengaluru** performing specials, hosting open mics, trying out new sets, and more.
**Music shows-** Looking for a way to unwind from the post-work blues? [Music shows](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/events/music-shows-Bengaluru) might do the trick! Experience handpicked gigs, bollywood, and concerts from a diverse choice of genres.
