Section Title: ## Find The Best Music Events & Concerts in Bengaluru Just For You
Content:
If musical and jam sessions are your thing and you are looking for such sessions, then you are at the right place. For those who enjoy online music events over closed place events, BookMyShow is here with modern solutions!
For all the music lovers out there who love attending music events, we have come up with a unique concept of organizing [music shows online](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/online-streaming-music-shows-Bengaluru) .
Section Title: ## Find The Best Music Events & Concerts in Bengaluru Just For You
Content:
Streaming online, you can now witness the craze of a concert and rockfest in 2026 in Bengaluru with an online ticket booking. Choose from different venues and you will see that entertainment has no boundaries in Bengaluru. With events such as **[Sunburn Holi Ft. KSHMR - Bengaluru](https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/sunburn-holi-bengaluru/ET00483369?webview=true) , [UN40: Music & Beyond](https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/un40-music-beyond/ET00480988?webview=true) & [CALVIN HARRIS - Live in Bengaluru](https://in.bookmyshow.com/events/calvin-harris-live-in-bengaluru/ET00461392?webview=true)** , get ready for the biggest music festivals of the year.
