Content:
Live events are thoughtfully divided into three main categories.
**Comedy events-** If you like to tickle your funny bone, comic relief can be your go-to option. Find the latest [](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/comedy-shows-Bengaluru) [comedy events](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/comedy-shows-bengaluru) by some of Bengaluru’s best comedians. Catch them in **Bengaluru** performing specials, hosting open mics, trying out new sets, and more.
**Music shows-** Looking for a way to unwind from the post-work blues? [Music shows](https://in.bookmyshow.com/explore/events/music-shows-Bengaluru) might do the trick! Experience handpicked gigs, bollywood, and concerts from a diverse choice of genres.
